text: Hilde Dobiasch (born 5 October 1954) is an Austrian former cyclist. She competed in the women's road race event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Austria Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
